title: Masters of Horror Composers Collection 1 (horror ost's)
description:
A small Collection of some of the best horror soundtracks
by some amazing composers such as 

Angelo Badalamenti = Twin Peaks
Claudio Simonetti = Mother of Tears
Danny Elfman = Sleepy Hollow
Ennio Morricone = Stendhal Syndrome
Fabio Frizzi = City of the Living Dead
Goblin = Phenomena
Jerry Goldsmith = Planet of the Apes
Jerry Komeda = Rosemarys Baby
Les Baxter = Dunwich Horror
Riz Ortolani = Cannibal Holacaust
Trevor Jones = Dark City
Walter Rizzati = House by the Cemetary
Phantasm
the Exorcist
